2017-07-20 15:58:58 --- DEBUG: {"message":"","data":{"auditState":2,"components":[{"text":"现在市面上的销售的金士顿存储产品可谓数不胜数，不少用户在选购存储产品的时候都会认准金士顿这个大品牌。毕竟金士顿的名气比较大，哪怕是不懂硬件的朋友也多多少少听过这个牌子。因此许多不法商家为了谋取暴力会制作并且售卖假金士顿产品，给消费者带来很多困扰。","type":"text"},{"text":"此前就有网友论坛上曝光，在网上购买了一款金士顿TF卡，竟然是假货，并且商家拒绝回应。","type":"text"},{"text":"","type":"image","url":"https:\/\/i-pre.meixincdn.com\/v1\/img\/T1nzYTB5xT1RXrhCrK.jpg","picture":{"url":"https:\/\/i-pre.meixincdn.com\/v1\/img\/T1nzYTB5xT1RXrhCrK.jpg","key":"T1nzYTB5xT1RXrhCrK","width":580,"height":326}},{"text":"该用户指出，他购买了一张16GBTF卡，结果只用了几个月就坏了。商家提出保修需要出来回运费，于是他直接找到全国联保的本地金士顿售后，结果经售后鉴定，该TF卡为假货，不予保修。","type":"text"},{"text":"假货泛滥的原因其实有很多方面，其中最主要的原因也无非是利润，仿冒存储产品的容量越大利润就越高，很多时候也因为消费者贪图小便宜而购买到假货。据透露，很多JS会把真货和假货放到一起售卖和任由消费者挑选，而且它们的开价是一样的，这也是为了让消费者觉得有讲价的空间，之后再把价钱压低，让消费者觉得十分优惠从而上当，但有的消费者还是会挑中假货。现在假货金士顿的仿冒技术非常高超，所以为了让广大消费者不买假货，DIY编辑部专门购买了一款假金士顿SSD产品，和真的SSD进行对比，下面我们仔细观察一下二者的区别。","type":"text"},{"text":"我们购买的产品型号为金士顿V300，一款市面上热销的SSD。首先我们先看一下产品的外包装有什么区别。","type":"text"},{"text":"","type":"image","url":"https:\/\/i-pre.meixincdn.com\/v1\/img\/T1KRATBsWT1RXrhCrK.jpg","picture":{"url":"https:\/\/i-pre.meixincdn.com\/v1\/img\/T1KRATBsWT1RXrhCrK.jpg","key":"T1KRATBsWT1RXrhCrK","width":640,"height":427}},{"text":"金士顿V300（左真右假）","type":"text"},{"text":"从产品外包装的正面来看，最大的区别就是假货没有防伪标签，另外就是假货包装的颜色和真货稍微有一点区别，但是如果没有对比，消费者很难区分这种颜色的差异。","type":"text"},{"text":"","type":"image","url":"https:\/\/i-pre.meixincdn.com\/v1\/img\/T1laATB_LT1RXrhCrK.jpg","picture":{"url":"https:\/\/i-pre.meixincdn.com\/v1\/img\/T1laATB_LT1RXrhCrK.jpg","key":"T1laATB_LT1RXrhCrK","width":640,"height":427}},{"text":"产品包装(左真右假）","type":"text"},{"text":"将包装打开后，可以发现颜色差异更加明显，并且真货印刷品质更好，画面清晰锐利，而假货就显得很粗糙了。","type":"text"},{"text":"","type":"image","url":"https:\/\/i-pre.meixincdn.com\/v1\/img\/T1NRWTBsVT1RXrhCrK.jpg","picture":{"url":"https:\/\/i-pre.meixincdn.com\/v1\/img\/T1NRWTBsVT1RXrhCrK.jpg","key":"T1NRWTBsVT1RXrhCrK","width":640,"height":427}},{"text":"包装细节（真）","type":"text"},{"text":"","type":"image","url":"https:\/\/i-pre.meixincdn.com\/v1\/img\/T1NXxTBvLT1RXrhCrK.jpg","picture":{"url":"https:\/\/i-pre.meixincdn.com\/v1\/img\/T1NXxTBvLT1RXrhCrK.jpg","key":"T1NXxTBvLT1RXrhCrK","width":640,"height":427}},{"text":"包装细节（假）","type":"text"},{"text":"细节方面，金士顿V300真货的印刷的“SOLID-STATEDRICE固态硬盘”下方的颜色与假货完全不同，并且从包装的边缘来看，真货的边缘更平滑，而假货的边缘比较毛糙。","type":"text"},{"text":"","type":"image","url":"https:\/\/i-pre.meixincdn.com\/v1\/img\/T1BFhTB5xv1RXrhCrK.jpg","picture":{"url":"https:\/\/i-pre.meixincdn.com\/v1\/img\/T1BFhTB5xv1RXrhCrK.jpg","key":"T1BFhTB5xv1RXrhCrK","width":640,"height":427}},{"text":"包装细节（真）","type":"text"},{"text":"","type":"image","url":"https:\/\/i-pre.meixincdn.com\/v1\/img\/T1eNYTB7ZT1RXrhCrK.jpg","picture":{"url":"https:\/\/i-pre.meixincdn.com\/v1\/img\/T1eNYTB7ZT1RXrhCrK.jpg","key":"T1eNYTB7ZT1RXrhCrK","width":640,"height":427}},{"text":"包装细节（假）","type":"text"},{"text":"字体印刷上,假货的印刷字体发虚,没有真货的质感好。","type":"text"},{"text":"","type":"image","url":"https:\/\/i-pre.meixincdn.com\/v1\/img\/T17yATBQdT1RXrhCrK.jpg","picture":{"url":"https:\/\/i-pre.meixincdn.com\/v1\/img\/T17yATBQdT1RXrhCrK.jpg","key":"T17yATBQdT1RXrhCrK","width":640,"height":427}},{"text":"包装背面（左真右假）","type":"text"},{"text":"产品包装的背面，下方的颜色差异也比较明显，假货的下方成黄色，而真货的下方颜色是偏灰色的。","type":"text"},{"text":"有关包装的对比就到这里了，下面我们看一下产品的差异。","type":"text"},{"text":"接下来我们进入产品对比，乍一看二者几乎一模一样。","type":"text"},{"text":"","type":"image","url":"https:\/\/i-pre.meixincdn.com\/v1\/img\/T1itATBQCT1RXrhCrK.jpg","picture":{"url":"https:\/\/i-pre.meixincdn.com\/v1\/img\/T1itATBQCT1RXrhCrK.jpg","key":"T1itATBQCT1RXrhCrK","width":640,"height":427}},{"text":"产品外观（左真右假）","type":"text"},{"text":"我们可以发现真货白底交接处有一条暗红色的长方形，而假货同样的位置只有纯黑色。","type":"text"},{"text":"","type":"image","url":"https:\/\/i-pre.meixincdn.com\/v1\/img\/T1NyWTBsZT1RXrhCrK.jpg","picture":{"url":"https:\/\/i-pre.meixincdn.com\/v1\/img\/T1NyWTBsZT1RXrhCrK.jpg","key":"T1NyWTBsZT1RXrhCrK","width":640,"height":427}},{"text":"产品外观（真）","type":"text"},{"text":"","type":"image","url":"https:\/\/i-pre.meixincdn.com\/v1\/img\/T1NzxTB_LT1RXrhCrK.jpg","picture":{"url":"https:\/\/i-pre.meixincdn.com\/v1\/img\/T1NzxTB_LT1RXrhCrK.jpg","key":"T1NzxTB_LT1RXrhCrK","width":640,"height":427}},{"text":"产品外观（假）","type":"text"},{"text":"将产品放大后,可以看出真货和假货除了120GB几个字的字体不太相同,其他地方都很难分辨。不过很快假货就会露出马脚。","type":"text"},{"text":"","type":"image","url":"https:\/\/i-pre.meixincdn.com\/v1\/img\/T1uNhTBQbT1RXrhCrK.jpg","picture":{"url":"https:\/\/i-pre.meixincdn.com\/v1\/img\/T1uNhTBQbT1RXrhCrK.jpg","key":"T1uNhTBQbT1RXrhCrK","width":640,"height":427}},{"text":"螺丝孔（真）","type":"text"},{"text":"","type":"image","url":"https:\/\/i-pre.meixincdn.com\/v1\/img\/T1eFYTB7KT1RXrhCrK.jpg","picture":{"url":"https:\/\/i-pre.meixincdn.com\/v1\/img\/T1eFYTB7KT1RXrhCrK.jpg","key":"T1eFYTB7KT1RXrhCrK","width":640,"height":427}},{"text":"螺丝孔（假）","type":"text"},{"text":"通过产品背部的螺丝孔，可以轻易的判断他们的真伪。真货的螺丝与螺丝孔很精准的结合了在一起，而假货的螺丝很明显有点歪，做工粗糙。","type":"text"},{"text":"","type":"image","url":"https:\/\/i-pre.meixincdn.com\/v1\/img\/T1_tATBybv1RXrhCrK.jpg","picture":{"url":"https:\/\/i-pre.meixincdn.com\/v1\/img\/T1_tATBybv1RXrhCrK.jpg","key":"T1_tATBybv1RXrhCrK","width":640,"height":427}},{"text":"螺丝类型（真）","type":"text"},{"text":"","type":"image","url":"https:\/\/i-pre.meixincdn.com\/v1\/img\/T1XaATByZv1RXrhCrK.jpg","picture":{"url":"https:\/\/i-pre.meixincdn.com\/v1\/img\/T1XaATByZv1RXrhCrK.jpg","key":"T1XaATByZv1RXrhCrK","width":640,"height":427}},{"text":"螺丝类型（假）","type":"text"},{"text":"撕开贴纸后，对比更明显了，真货的包装粘的很紧，假货的包装很轻易就能撕开。并且真货使用的是六角带顶针螺丝，而假货用的就是普通的十字螺丝。","type":"text"},{"text":"最后我们对真假金士顿进行拆解，结果非常意外。","type":"text"},{"text":"","type":"image","url":"https:\/\/i-pre.meixincdn.com\/v1\/img\/T1NtWTB4Jv1RXrhCrK.jpg","picture":{"url":"https:\/\/i-pre.meixincdn.com\/v1\/img\/T1NtWTB4Jv1RXrhCrK.jpg","key":"T1NtWTB4Jv1RXrhCrK","width":640,"height":427}},{"text":"拆解图（假）","type":"text"},{"text":"拆开外壳后，可以看到假货的PCB板只有一半，PCB板边缘非常粗糙。颗粒上印着不明数字，看来做假者不是很用心呀！","type":"text"},{"text":"","type":"image","url":"https:\/\/i-pre.meixincdn.com\/v1\/img\/T10NxTBgbT1RXrhCrK.jpg","picture":{"url":"https:\/\/i-pre.meixincdn.com\/v1\/img\/T10NxTBgbT1RXrhCrK.jpg","key":"T10NxTBgbT1RXrhCrK","width":640,"height":427}},{"text":"拆解图（真）","type":"text"},{"text":"真货的PCB板很完整，共有8个颗粒，颗粒上有金士顿的英文拼写。","type":"text"},{"text":"","type":"image","url":"https:\/\/i-pre.meixincdn.com\/v1\/img\/T18FhTBQDT1RXrhCrK.jpg","picture":{"url":"https:\/\/i-pre.meixincdn.com\/v1\/img\/T18FhTBQDT1RXrhCrK.jpg","key":"T18FhTBQDT1RXrhCrK","width":640,"height":427}},{"text":"拆解对比","type":"text"},{"text":"放在一起对比，可以看出假货缩水十分严重。","type":"text"},{"text":"小结：","type":"text"},{"text":"有关真假金士顿SSD的对比就到这里了，大家可以看到假货的做工缩水非常严重，除了外包装模仿的比较像以外，其他地方能省则省，购买这样的产品质量得不到保证，售后服务也是空谈，损失金钱事小，丢失数据事大。所以大家在购买存储产品时，一定要从正规途径购买，如果想鉴别自己购买的产品的真伪可以在金士顿的官方微信进行验证，千万不可贪图一时省事，不然很容易买到假货。","type":"text"}],"createTime":1494232783304,"extTopicType":0,"group":{"auditState":2,"createTime":1490006307523,"createrId":100037483561,"icon":"https:\/\/i-pre.meixincdn.com\/T1qtYTBmDv1RXrhCrK.jpg","id":"mx1000374835611488957897831","introduction":"联调测试圈子","isPublic":true,"memberQuantity":14,"name":"联调测试圈子","topicQuantity":237},"groupId":"mx1000374835611488957897831","id":"59102ecfd15f8c7ac1e2f6f4","isEssence":false,"isPublic":true,"isUpper":false,"lastReplyTime":1494232783304,"name":"同时拆解真假金士顿SSD 结果出人意料","replyQuantity":0,"style":0,"subReplyQuantity":0,"updateTime":1494232783304,"user":{"id":100037483561,"nickname":"gm_153^_^8266jch","gender":null,"facePicUrl":"http:\/\/gfs11.atguat.net.cn\/T1o4KTBTWQ1RCvBVdK.png","referralCode":"XcMz8qLv","isXPop":0,"isMShop":0,"email":null,"birthday":null,"xpopRefereeId":null,"registerTime":null,"userSign":"","emailActivated":false,"mobileActivated":true},"memberType":1,"expertInfo":{"isExpert":false},"userCollection":{"result":false},"topicCollectionQuantity":0,"userOwnedGroupQuantity":{"ownedGroupQuantity":0},"userOwnedTopicQuantity":{"ownedTopicQuantity":263},"pageview":135875,"pageviewText":"13万+"},"debug":"STEP(1)  MSG(Load json: \